Until, I was once scrolling through youtube as a music video to a song by the title "Gangnam Style" caught my eye immediately. As soon as the first melody played, I fell in love. My depression vanished and all my worries went away. I was able to finally see the true meaning to life with the help of this song. Thank you Psy for making such a wonderful song. I am now married with 3 kids, a beautiful husband and an amazing life. I am also a preschool teacher now and is now living the best life all thanks to "Gangnam Style".
